{"tid":1632311,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 從大學生角度話你知點解大專咁多次罷課不成功","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T19:01:29.000Z","uid":148983,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0cf5b823ba629768489e6958875ccd59cdd2cd23","tid":1632311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>講嘅只係其中一間大專嘅個人觀察，其他大專可能有唔同，歡迎補充<br />\n利申Shitty，恥與為伍</strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n好多人都不停屌點解大專學生成日唔響應罷課，除咗暴大其他大專又好似冇咩聲氣咁，有見及此，小弟決定出post分析同解釋下點解次次都雷聲大雨點少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 本地生人數不足</span></ins></strong><br />\n冇錯，第一日罷課好多人去咗百萬大道集會好曡馬，但大家忘記咗呢度係咁多大專合計人數，其實諗返轉頭其實咁多大專先咁多人好似唔係非常多咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實上，讀大專嘅人會知道現時大學充滿非本地生，不論外國人，定中国人都充滿大專校園，即使本地大專生全部黃去罷課都未必會真正影響到課堂進行（而事實上小弟見過有藍嘅大專生） <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 教授</span></ins></strong><br />\n喂，教授都關事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇錯，正正就係教授出曬事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟就讀於一間好中意打飛機嘅大專，校長長期唔見人，喺爵士過身先出現，平時搵個藍絲副校出緊急通告。試問一個連政治同生活無法分割都唔明，叫人唔好將政治帶入校園嘅校長點會理學生吖，起碼隔離暴大校長都肯出嚟拍下檯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺一個咁嘅環境下，由於年年要刷Rank打飛機所以會有好多非本地教授來往，莫講非本地知道又支持我哋嘅，本地黃嘅更加喺少之又少。人哋出個要求100%出席率嘅課程，你叫大專生唔上，等於斷送自己GPA <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你會話GPA又如何，但大佬吖我都想畢業㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 宣傳嚴重不足</span></ins></strong><br />\n之前大家都略有所聞大專發起兩星期罷課，坦白講我同身邊朋友都淨係知道開學頭兩日罷課（頭兩日只係指中學生，唔係大學生），心理上冇準備，加上本地+非本地嘅教授+學生好多都唔知到罷課兩星期，更唔知我哋罷課原因，後來追查發現學生會出咗篇聲明就算，由此可見文宣繼續不足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">大專罷課成功方程式</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">校舍貼滿文宣&gt;人肉解釋&gt;多學生響應&gt;教授支援=罷課成功</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">從來冇唔夠文宣，只係冇人貼，傳送門：</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5aa49892\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a></span>"},{"pid":"9b764d081d3a47858612018f33d653dafb1e9df8","tid":1632311,"uid":148983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">從來冇唔夠文宣，只係冇人貼，傳送門：</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5aa49892\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a></span>"},{"pid":"eb49ca224e4e4d77ba5c85fde7fedf8ca0fe50d2","tid":1632311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">從來冇唔夠文宣，只係冇人貼，傳送門：</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5aa49892\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a></span>"},{"pid":"06ae6130926af0496de89fbdf4766563e6620a3c","tid":1632311,"ui